definitions.definition: For all of a given time interval; throughout; in; pending.
examples: I lived with my parents during the 1970s.
This shop, which was among the few able to stay open during the war, is closed during the whole of August.

definitions.definition: At any time or period within a given time interval.
examples: I lived with my parents at several points during the 1980s.
Many of the best examples were produced during the Restoration.

main_definition: For all of a given time interval; throughout; in; pending.
secondary_definitions: At any time or period within a given time interval.
